      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 3.2L inline-six features a fully overhauled double-VANOS system and precise valve lash adjustments, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the 8,000 RPM powerband. The Getrag Type D six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, transferring torque to a factory-spec limited-slip differential with zero lash. The chassis has been proactively addressed with subframe reinforcement plates, maintaining original torsional rigidity. Finished with a pristine undercarriage and no fluid weeping, this specimen retains its factory-intended kinematics and throttle response. A turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
